gyms.name: Republic of Domination
gyms.about: Republic of Domination is a vibrant calisthenics sports club in Bengaluru, where people of all ages and fitness levels can come together to learn and compete in calisthenics. With state-of-the-art facilities, the club offers something for everyone. Republic of Domination also offers a wide range of fitness classes, such as calisthenics and yoga, to help members achieve their fitness goals. Whether you're a seasoned athlete or just starting out, Republic of Domination is the perfect place to stay active and have fun.

gyms.name: CaliOG
gyms.about: Engage in real-life movements for functional strength and mobility. Build a strong and stable core foundation for better balance and posture. Develop overall strength with multi-muscle group exercises. Customizable training for all fitness levels and goals.

gyms.name: Kineto Calisthenics Park
gyms.about: Kineto Calisthenics Park was founded in Jan 15 ,2023 with the motto to spread the calisthenics among the people of South bangalore & encourage the athlete from South India to get trained and participate in competition across India to step into the global stage.

gyms.name: CaliBAF - The Calisthenics Studio
gyms.about: CaliBAF studio is designed to help you push your limits and achieve your fitness goals. Learn from experts and get top-notch guidance. Join CALIBAF calisthenics community & get EXPERT Coaches who can provide personalized advice and training programs.

gyms.name: Limitless Calisthenics
gyms.about: Calisthenics academy based in Bangalore. Learn from certified coaches and national athletes.

gyms.name: The Movement Fitness Centre
gyms.about: At movement gyms, you will get to experience an environment where you are free to work out the way you like. They have trained professionals ready to step in and teach you how to use the equipments.
